Seq1.ReceiverContent: Good afternoon. Thanks for calling Crofton Family Practice. This is Dominic. How may I assist you for the day?

Seq2.CallerContent: Hi there. I was just in to see Dr. Williams and she wanted me to pick up a prescription at Target that she sent in, but they said they haven't gotten it.
Seq2.ReceiverContent: Okay. Regarding that, let me transfer the call to a friend this month. They'll help you out with this. Kindly stay online. You have a great day.

Seq3.ReceiverContent:
Hello. You have reached the nurse line. If this is an emergency, please hang up and dial 9-1-1.
If you're calling for a prescription refill, please leave a detailed message with the drug name, the milligrams, and your pharmacy information.
Please allow 72 hours for your refills to be processed. Leave us a message and we'll get back to you as soon as we can. Thank you and have a good day.
